sub_title:
Student of International Development Management 
University of Applied Sciences Van Hall Larenstein

- Meaningful and adventurous humanist
summary:
Adventurous humanist who empowers in a meaningful and well-being driven way and believes in each person's own wisdom and capabilities.
I create contentment by clarifying desire and converting it into action. As a guide, I aim to guide people in achieving better well-being.

I am an International Development Management student which hopes to bring good to the world through technological development, creation of opportunities and social cooperation. For this I am always looking for new opportunities!

I would describe myself as: 
- Purpose seeking 
- Goal oriented, but with love for the journey
- Honesty 
- Family & Friends 
- Competence through gaining experience
- Curiosity
- Solidarity
- Social
- Gratitude
- Adventurous
